==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-əʊt|-əʊt]]

=== Noun ===
'''oat''' (Plural: [[oats]])

# A widely cultivated cereal grass, ''[[Avena sativa]]''.
# The seeds of the oat, harvested as a food crop. Used also in form [[oats]].

====Scientific names====
*[[Avena sativa]]

